io.debezium.relational.ddl

Class DdlParserSql2003

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.debezium.relational.ddl.AbstractDdlParser
      • io.debezium.relational.ddl.LegacyDdlParser
        • io.debezium.relational.ddl.DdlParserSql2003
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DdlParser

    @NotThreadSafe
public class DdlParserSql2003
extends LegacyDdlParser
    A parser for DDL statements.

    See the BNF Grammar for ISO/IEC 9075-2:2003 for the grammar supported by this parser.
